## Get Existing Account

> Example Request

```shell
curl <%=@api_prefix%>/2/account/11 \
 -H "W-Token: <%=@wiw_token%>"
```
```php
<?php
$wiw = new Wheniwork("<%=@wiw_token%>");
$result = $wiw->get("account/11");
?>
```

> Example Response

